edu.common.dynamicextensions.domaininterface
Interface AssociationInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Association
public interface AssociationInterface

This interface contains all the information regarding association between the entities. The association may be of different types like one-to-many,many-to-many or from source - destination, bidirectional.Entity object contains association collection.Each object in association collection represents association of the entity with other entity. Using the information of association object different constraints are added in the dynamically created tables.

Author:
sujay_narkar
